data.description: 2019 Townhome in Asturia, 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 Bathrooms, oversized detached 2 car garage, amazing open floor plan with 9 foot ceilings, from the moment you walk in, you want to stay, so clean, comfortable & relaxing Vibe: Less than 40 minutes to St. Pete Beach in Florida was named The #1 Beach in America and the Fifth Best Beach In The World, Asturia has multiple trails, playgrounds, picnic areas, dog parks and an impressive community center with luxurious swimming pool and fully equipped fitness center (free weights, strength training machines, cardio equipment). Pool also features lap lanes and beach entry.
